border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(92, 157, 255); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n   <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">不退转，常人思惟难以理解的地方在于，这本身并不是稳定的。或者说恰恰相反，是极其不稳定的。</p> \n  </blockquote> \n  <blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(92, 157, 255); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n   <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">现象仍然在生起，经验质地依旧在不断流转变换。但是却不会再粘滞于思维的叙述，不会再粘滞于人生故事。故事好像依旧在发生，但实际又完全超越了思维的解释。</p> \n  </blockquote> \n  <blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(92, 157, 255); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n   <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">因为明白了经验质地的发散性，明白了思维叙述的发散性，明白了表相看似呈现，而实相却远远超越这些心智效应。</p> \n  </blockquote> \n  <blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(92, 157, 255); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n   <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">所以，现象中的经验时时刻刻生起吧，而一切经验质地都可以是无害的。不再定义“有害”、“无害”这对看似对立的幻觉概念，不再觉得真的有“已完成的”与“待到达”的状态，不再以为有“久远的过去”和“看似遥远的未来”······那么还为什么要“修行”呢？</p> \n  </blockquote> \n  <blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(92, 157, 255); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n   <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">看似还在现象中，看似还有一个“人”在世界上生活，但那些都不过是心智编织的故事。心智效应时刻在显现，不需要停下心智效应。想要去停下心智效应，意味着隐约觉得有一个主体，可以去主宰（控制）这一切现象。而这个主体性，仍然是心智效应的一部分。</p> \n  </blockquote> \n  <blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(92, 157, 255); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n   <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">心智效应发生，但也只是看似在发生。而区分出心智效应的那位，恰恰就是心智效应本身。时刻穿透了心智的叙述，和明白心智叙述的发散性其实是同义词。此即“不迷”，即“明白”。</p> \n  </blockquote> \n  <blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(92, 157, 255); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n   <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">看似有心智效应，但又时时刻刻发散掉；甚至无法确定有没有“心智效应”这一回事。那么这一切到底是什么呢？世界的真相到底是什么呢？</p> \n  </blockquote> \n  <blockquote class=\"multiquote-1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 10px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: solid; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgb(92, 157, 255); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block; overflow-x: auto; overflow-y: auto;\"> <span style=\"display: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\"></span> \n   <p style=\"text-indent: 0em; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">心智叙述已经发散了，就好像堕入无底洞中。周围完全没有参照物，只好像在不停下坠，下坠，下坠······</p> \n  </blockquote> \n </section> \n</section>",
